      d="M 0,0 L 542,0 C 572,0 588,34 577,88 C 566,142 536,180 506,226 C 476,272 455,306 434,343 Q 410,382 378,407 Q 337,434 295,452 Q 243,473 190,482 C 126,493 60,483 20,458 C -4,442 0,412 0,378 Z"
      fill="#2F95EE"></path>
